## ğŸ› ï¸ Development

### Setup Development Environment

```bash
# Clone repository
git clone https://github.com/python-weaver/python-weaver.git
cd python-weaver

# Install in development mode
pip install -e .[dev]

# Run tests
pytest

# Run with coverage
pytest --cov=weaver --cov-report=html
```

